content:
Mu rwego rwo kwirinda indwara ya Malariya, bagomba kugirira isuku aho
batuye batema ibihuru bikikije urugo, bakanasiba ibyobo amazi ashobora 
kurekamo kuko aribyo bituma iyo mibu yororoka.
